parameters.content:
# üé® n8n AI Agent Interface Template

Beautiful web UI for your AI agents - no frontend skills needed!

## ‚ö° Quick Setup (2 workflows)

### Workflow 1: Display Interface (3 nodes)
```
Webhook (GET) ‚Üí Code Node ‚Üí Respond to Webhook
```
1. **Webhook**: GET, path `/your-interface`
2. **Code Node**: Paste entire `main.js`
3. **Respond**: Binary, property `data`

### Workflow 2: Process Requests (5+ nodes)
```
Webhook (POST) ‚Üí Switch ‚Üí AI Agents ‚Üí Code ‚Üí Respond
```
1. **Webhook (POST)**: path `/webhook-endpoint`
2. **Switch**: Route by `{{ $json.body.agent_type }}`
3. **AI Agents**: 4 nodes (general, database, web, rag)
4. **Code Node**:
```javascript
const webhookData = $('Webhook').first().json.body;
const aiResponse = $input.first().json;

return [{
  json: {
    response: aiResponse.output || aiResponse.text || aiResponse.response,
    agent_type: webhookData.agent_type
  }
}];
```
5. **Respond**: Return JSON

## üîß Update in main.js

**Line 847**: Change webhook URL
```javascript
const WEBHOOK_URL = '/webhook/webhook-endpoint';
```

## ‚ú® Features
‚úÖ Real-time AI responses 
‚úÖ Loading animations 
‚úÖ 4 agent types 
‚úÖ Dark/light mode 
‚úÖ Mobile responsive
